{"word":"G2799 - κλαίω - klaíō - klah'-yo - Bewail","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κλαίω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">klaíō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">klah'-yo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bewail</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அழு"},{"paragraph":"to mourn, weep, lament"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Of uncertain affinity; to <i>sob</i>, that is, <i>wail</i> aloud (whereas <a href=\"#/G1145 - δακρύω - dakrýō - dak-roo'-o/1145\">G1145</a> is rather to <i>cry</i> silently): - bewail. weep.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2799/2799\">G2799</a>, <a href=\"#/G2805/2805\">G2805</a>"}]}